headline: Cincinnati Financial (NASDAQ:CINF) Reports Bullish Q3
summary: Property casualty insurer Cincinnati Financial (NASDAQ:CINF) reported revenue ahead of Wall Street’s expectations in Q3 CY2025, with sales up 12.2% year on year to $3.73 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.85 per share was 38.4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
